data.title: "THIS IS ME" Color Run
meta_keywords: "THIS IS ME" Color Run Huntingtown tickets
data.meta_description: Eventbrite - Calvert Alliance Against Substance Abuse, Inc. (CAASA) presents "THIS IS ME" Color Run - Sunday, September 15, 2024 at The Calverton School, Huntingtown, MD. Find event and ticket information.
data.text:
üéâ Join us for an explosion of color and positivity at the "THIS IS ME" Color Run on September 15th! This isn't just any run; it's a celebration of YOUth empowerment, promoting happiness, health, and a substance-free lifestyle.

üëï Get ready to rock your free t-shirts, sunglasses, bandanas, and bracelets as you dash through vibrant clouds of color! üé® Groove to awesome beats, dive into thrilling games, and experience the joy of being your true, authentic self.

But wait, there's more! üåü For just a $20 registration fee, you can secure your spot in this unforgettable event. Plus, it's absolutely free for those three (3) and younger, ensuring that everyone can join in on the fun! Those who are three (3) and younger do not receive t-shirts. Those registered by August 10th are guaranteed a t-shirt and color run swag bag.

Local youth groups will host the color blast stations, adding an extra layer of community spirit and giving back. Every burst of color helps raise funds for their invaluable programs, supporting our youth in reaching their full potential.

We're excited to share that "THE NOVEL BAKERY" will be joining us this year. They have an amazing selection of scones, muffins, hot/cold coffee and tea and specialty coffee and tea drinks. Check out their Facebook page to learn more about this local business from Chesapeake Beach, Maryland.

Mark your calendars and spread the word ‚Äî because on September 15th, we're all about embracing individuality, supporting local youth initiatives, and living life to the fullest.
